description:
The final season of "Snooki & JWOWW" follows the dynamic duo as they deal with the craziest adventure of all - motherhood. Snooki and JWOWW have always joked about their desire to be pregnant together, and it's finally happened! With both girls pregnant (JWOWW's first and Snooki's second) and living next door to each other, the girls are growing up before our eyes. There's always time for fun, whether they're attending yoga class together, making sushi for the boys, or preparing for Snooki's upcoming wedding!
